The Real... Andy Williams is an album compilation by Andy Williams which was released Dec 20, 2011 on the Sony Music label. Though his commercial peak was in the '60s and '70s, Williams has continued to stay busy over the decades by touring, recording and headlining his own Moon River Theater in Branson, MO. He also remains popular in the UK and Europe, where he has frequently toured over the years. This triple disc set features many of his classics songs including 'Moon River', 'Can't Get Used To Losing You' and many more. Also included is a dozen Christmas favorites.
